  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA263-kiḷavi">itu ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻi talaimakaṉai varaivu kaṭāyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante urged HIM for marriage when [he] was behind the fence.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA263">
<l>            piṟaivaṉap piḻanta nutalum yāḻani</l>
<l>            ṉiṟaivarai nillā vaḷaiyu maṟaiyā</l>
<l>            tūralar tūṟṟuṅ kauvaiyu nāṇiṭ</l>
<l>            ṭuraiyavark kuraiyā māyiṉu miraivēṭṭuk</l>
<l>            kaṭuñcūl vayavoṭu kāṉa leytātu </l>
<l>            kaḻaṉi yoḻinta koṭuvāyp pēṭaikku</l>
<l>            muṭamutir nārai kaṭaṉmī ṉoyyu</l>
<l>            mellam pulampaṟ kaṇṭunilai cellāk</l>
<l>            karappavuṅ karappavuṅ kaimmik</l>
<l>            kuraitta tōḻi yuṇka ṇīrē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent2">Even if we do not tell him a word,</l>
<l rend="indent">out of shame for [our] forehead that has lost [its] crescent moon beauty</l>
<l rend="indent">and [our] bangles that won’t stay on the joints and the rumour</l>
<l rend="indent2">that spreads with gossip in the village without concealing,</l>
<l rend="indent3">upon seeing the soft man from the lonely [shore],</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the lame ageing heron carries fish from the sea</l>
<l rend="indent">to [its] female with bent beak that stayed behind in the fields,</l>
<l rend="indent">not reaching the seashore grove with the cravings of advanced pregnancy,</l>
<l rend="indent">desiring prey</l>
<l rend="indent4">– though hiding and hiding [this] untenable state</l>
<l>the waters in [our] kajal eyes have exceeded [and] told him, friend.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
